            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Initially the school staff/management was good. Now a days it's very difficult to manage to pay a single quarter fees since there is a hike of fees by around 25% in a single year. Hike by 50%  in a school books . How a common man afford such type of fees.\nI think it is a crime to get the children educated from a private schools now a day by common people.",
